Package: multiplot
Title: Emulate Statistical Plot Styles of Nine Software Packages and an Academic Style
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R:
    person("Shuqiong", "Su", , "sushuqiong@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: One-stop ggplot2 extension that emulates the default plot styles
    of nine statistical graphing software packages plus an additional academic
    publication style. A single ggchoice() call applies the complete visual
    style (theme + colour/fill scales) for GraphPad Prism, SPSS, OriginPro,
    Stata (s2color), SigmaPlot, JMP, MATLAB, Minitab, MedCalc, and classic
    academic (AMS/Science) output.
